Paper: hep-th/0007025

Date: 2000-07-04

Title: Higgs mechanism in the Randall-Sundrum model

Authors: A. Flachi and D. J. Toms

Comments: 8 pages, 1 figure

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B491 (2000) 157-160

We consider the dimensional reduction of a bulk scalar field in theRandall-Sundrum model. By allowing the scalar field to be non-minimally coupledto the spacetime curvature we show that it is possible to generate spontaneoussymmetry breaking on the brane.